      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0035"/>Herrn</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype">Dr. Arthur Schnitzler</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb168940">XVIII. Spöttelga<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>se 7</rs>.</hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="HS.NZ85.1.3175_0036"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs></hi>, <date when="1906-09-14"><hi rend="latintype">14. Sept</hi></date>. <salute>Lieber Freund,</salute> Bi<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>t Du in <rs type="place" ref="#pmb50">Wien</rs>? Und wenn ja, – wann darf ich Dich <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03250-1"/>be<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>uchen<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03250-1">Ein Treffen kam nicht zustande, da sich <rs type="person" ref="#pmb2121">Schnitzler</rs> zwischen <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1906-09-10" subtype="date-only"/> und <ref type="schnitzler-tagebuch" target="1906-09-20" subtype="date-only"/> auf dem <rs type="place" ref="#pmb189">Semmering</rs> aufhielt. Siehe auch <ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L03251"/>.</note>?</p><closer>Herzl. Gruß! <lb/>Dein <signed>Paul Goldmann</signed></closer><postscript><p rend="right"><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb255">Grand Hotel</rs></hi>.</p></postscript></div>
      </body>
